Interstate Motors Is Located At: 134 1/2 Commerce Ave, La Grange GA 30241

     Interstate Motors is a family owned and operated independent automobile dealer in LaGrange Georgia.  Our goal is to put every customer into the car of their choice.  And no one does it with more frequency than Interstate Motors.  Everyone is approved at Interstate Motors!

     At Interstate Motors, we have grown from our humble beginnings in a 300 square foot trailer to a 3000 square foot building with a show room.  However, no matter the size of the building or the size of our sales team, our mission remains the same. We want to create a better quality of life by helping customers rebuild their credit with the car of their choice so one day they can have the car of their dreams.

      The auto loan landscape has changed dramatically over the last 10 years.  In the past, if you had a car loan go bad you would be stuck with high interest rates and ‘Buy Here Pay Here’ dealers for the rest of your life.  At Interstate Motors, we are able to obtain bank financing for ALL of our customers.  Re-establishing your credit can save you tens of thousands of dollars over your lifetime.  Every customer is different and every budget is different.  That is why we have lenders for all walks of credit.  Good credit, bad credit, no credit and everything in between.

      We typically carry 40-50 quality pre-owned vehicles in our inventory.  If we don’t have it, we can find it.  Interstate Motors is conveniently located less than an hour from Atlanta, Columbus and Montgomery.

     Come visit us at our 2 locations:  218 Commerce Ave & 1304 LaFayette Parkway, both in LaGrange, GA.


Please feel free to call us at (706) 884 -2336 or send us an email using the form on the "Contact Us Page." 

You can reach our 1304 LaFayette Parkway office at (706) 756 - 1797.
